1
00:00:00,670 --> 00:00:01,976
<Default><b>[♪ Joyful music]</b></Default>

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:03,016
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] This room</b></Default>

3
00:00:03,040 --> 00:00:05,306
<Default><b>should be more
than big enough for all of us.</b></Default>

4
00:00:05,330 --> 00:00:06,435
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] Even so</b></Default>

5
00:00:06,459 --> 00:00:09,880
<Default><b>I'm afraid this room is for you
and you alone, Shield Hero.</b></Default>

6
00:00:10,210 --> 00:00:10,880
<Default><b>No fair!</b></Default>

7
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:13,240
<Default><b>I want to stay
right here with Master.</b></Default>

8
00:00:13,419 --> 00:00:16,699
<Default><b>[SERVANT] We've already prepared
another room for your servants.</b></Default>

9
00:00:17,129 --> 00:00:18,436
<Default><b>I'm sure you're
wondering</b></Default>

10
00:00:18,460 --> 00:00:20,765
<Default><b>what you'll be doing
for the rest of the day.</b></Default>

11
00:00:20,789 --> 00:00:23,829
<Default><b>Once you've gotten acquainted
with everything in your room</b></Default>

12
00:00:23,879 --> 00:00:26,515
<Default><b>we'll have you change
into Siltvelt formal wear.</b></Default>

13
00:00:26,539 --> 00:00:29,710
<Default><b>It's customary when attending
a banquet like the one tonight.</b></Default>

14
00:00:29,829 --> 00:00:30,869
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

15
00:00:31,129 --> 00:00:33,805
<Default><b>But before all that, we'll have
a bath drawn for you.</b></Default>

16
00:00:33,829 --> 00:00:35,936
<Default><b>It shouldn't take more
than a few minutes.</b></Default>

17
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:38,686
<Default><b>It feels like they're pretending
we don't even exist.</b></Default>

18
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:39,579
<Default><b>It sure does.</b></Default>

19
00:00:39,670 --> 00:00:41,476
<Default><b>There's still time
till the banquet.</b></Default>

20
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:44,055
<Default><b>We should go out and
explore the town while we can.</b></Default>

21
00:00:44,079 --> 00:00:46,960
<Default><b>Thanks, but I want to be on
standby in the next room.</b></Default>

22
00:00:47,039 --> 00:00:50,226
<Default><b>If something happens to Master
Naofumi, I have to protect him.</b></Default>

23
00:00:50,250 --> 00:00:54,250
<Default><b>Oh, come on. It'll be just fine.
Let's go see the town.</b></Default>

24
00:00:55,039 --> 00:00:55,579
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

25
00:00:55,750 --> 00:00:56,579
<Default><b>You know what?</b></Default>

26
00:00:56,710 --> 00:00:58,476
<Default><b>I think that's
a great idea.</b></Default>

27
00:00:58,500 --> 00:00:59,500
<Default><b>Yay!</b></Default>

28
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:02,500
<Default><b>I wonder if the booze
is any good around here.</b></Default>

29
00:01:02,750 --> 00:01:05,110
<Default><b>[FILO] What are we waiting for?
Let's go!</b></Default>

30
00:01:05,329 --> 00:01:06,209
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] But…</b></Default>

31
00:01:06,290 --> 00:01:07,170
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] But?</b></Default>

32
00:01:07,250 --> 00:01:08,750
<Default><b>[startled gasps]</b></Default>

33
00:01:10,420 --> 00:01:12,250
<Default><b>Raphy stays
here with me.</b></Default>

34
00:01:12,670 --> 00:01:13,670
<Default><b>Raphy!</b></Default>

35
00:01:15,329 --> 00:01:17,049
<Default><b>[♪ Opening music begins]</b></Default>

36
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:25,920
<Default><b>THE RISING OF
THE SHIELD HERO</b></Default>

37
00:02:42,669 --> 00:02:44,379
<Default><b>[♪ opening music ends]</b></Default>

38
00:02:45,919 --> 00:02:48,379
<Default><b>EPISODE 2:
OFFICIAL WELCOME</b></Default>

39
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:49,330
<Default><b>What a pain.</b></Default>

40
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:50,556
<Default><b>The way things stand</b></Default>

41
00:02:50,580 --> 00:02:53,540
<Default><b>this country might be more
of a headache than I thought.</b></Default>

42
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:54,726
<Default><b>Right, Raphy?</b></Default>

43
00:02:54,750 --> 00:02:55,870
<Default><b>[squeaks]</b></Default>

44
00:02:58,250 --> 00:02:59,370
<Default><b>[squeaks]</b></Default>

45
00:02:59,629 --> 00:03:01,109
<Default><b>What is it, Raphy?</b></Default>

46
00:03:02,129 --> 00:03:03,729
<Default><b>That's a cool shield.</b></Default>

47
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,120
<Default><b>Let's see.</b></Default>

48
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,400
<Default><b>Its skills are</b></Default>

49
00:03:07,539 --> 00:03:10,539
<Default><b>beast transformation
and territory reform.</b></Default>

50
00:03:11,250 --> 00:03:12,290
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

51
00:03:13,250 --> 00:03:15,169
<Default><b>[bells chiming]</b></Default>

52
00:03:25,330 --> 00:03:27,010
<Default><b>[♪ Joyful, chill music]</b></Default>

53
00:03:27,129 --> 00:03:29,750
<Default><b>Wow! That looks yummy.</b></Default>

54
00:03:30,539 --> 00:03:32,710
<Default><b>This town is fabulous</b></Default>

55
00:03:32,789 --> 00:03:34,169
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

56
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:36,430
<Default><b>Anything catch your eye?</b></Default>

57
00:03:39,419 --> 00:03:40,726
<Default><b>Judging from this statue</b></Default>

58
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:42,936
<Default><b>it seems like they know
how to show respect</b></Default>

59
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,476
<Default><b>for Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

60
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:46,330
<Default><b>I hope he's okay.</b></Default>

61
00:03:50,629 --> 00:03:52,515
<Default><b>These all look
really yummy too.</b></Default>

62
00:03:52,539 --> 00:03:55,000
<Default><b>I don't know about you</b></Default>

63
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:57,355
<Default><b>If things keep
going smoothly…</b></Default>

64
00:03:57,379 --> 00:04:00,460
<Default><b>Master Naofumi's territory
might look like this someday.</b></Default>

65
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:03,306
<Default><b>Just let me know whenever
you're ready to order.</b></Default>

66
00:04:03,330 --> 00:04:04,650
<Default><b>- Okay.
- Okay.</b></Default>

67
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:07,500
<Default><b>Huh? They
forgot their waters.</b></Default>

68
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:08,605
<Default><b>[people whispering]</b></Default>

69
00:04:08,629 --> 00:04:09,829
<Default><b>Disgusting.</b></Default>

70
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,080
<Default><b>I wish they would
get out of here.</b></Default>

71
00:04:12,629 --> 00:04:15,869
<Default><b>Now I understand why you were so
reluctant to leave the castle.</b></Default>

72
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:18,855
<Default><b>He's been acting like this
the whole time we've been here.</b></Default>

73
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:20,935
<Default><b>You let it get to you
too much, brother.</b></Default>

74
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:23,266
<Default><b>It's wonderful to have
so many types of people</b></Default>

75
00:04:23,290 --> 00:04:26,420
<Default><b>living together, but I'm sure
things are complicated.</b></Default>

76
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:29,340
<Default><b>Things are never quite
as simple as they seem to be.</b></Default>

77
00:04:29,629 --> 00:04:31,516
<Default><b>We need to learn
all that we can</b></Default>

78
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:34,460
<Default><b>And then report back to Naofumi
everything we find out.</b></Default>

79
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,040
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

80
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:45,959
<Default><b>Feels relaxing,
right, Raphy?</b></Default>

81
00:04:46,329 --> 00:04:47,329
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

82
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,000
<Default><b>[bubbling]</b></Default>

83
00:04:56,379 --> 00:04:57,379
<Default><b>Ah?</b></Default>

84
00:04:58,579 --> 00:04:59,726
<Default><b>APHRODISIAC DETECTED</b></Default>

85
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:00,579
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

86
00:05:00,670 --> 00:05:01,910
<Default><b>Aphrodisiac?</b></Default>

87
00:05:03,379 --> 00:05:06,129
<Default><b>What the hell is that about?
So much for relaxing.</b></Default>

88
00:05:07,250 --> 00:05:08,476
<Default><b>[female laughter]</b></Default>

89
00:05:08,500 --> 00:05:09,620
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

90
00:05:10,209 --> 00:05:13,209
<Default><b>[women clamoring,
approaching]</b></Default>

91
00:05:15,629 --> 00:05:17,540
<Default><b>Shield Hero!</b></Default>

92
00:05:17,709 --> 00:05:20,079
<Default><b>Shield Hero!
Shield Hero!</b></Default>

93
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:21,805
<Default><b>Wait, wait, wait!</b></Default>

94
00:05:21,829 --> 00:05:23,069
<Default><b>Shield Hero!</b></Default>

95
00:05:23,540 --> 00:05:24,935
<Default><b>Stay away from me!</b></Default>

96
00:05:24,959 --> 00:05:26,279
<Default><b>Meteor Shield!</b></Default>

97
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,480
<Default><b>[women clamoring]</b></Default>

98
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:31,879
<Default><b>Open up!</b></Default>

99
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,520
<Default><b>I thought you want someone
to wash your back?</b></Default>

100
00:05:35,629 --> 00:05:36,726
<Default><b>Portal Shield!</b></Default>

101
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,055
<Default><b>PORTAL SHIELD
UNAVAILABLE</b></Default>

102
00:05:38,079 --> 00:05:39,266
<Default><b>Unavailable?</b></Default>

103
00:05:39,290 --> 00:05:41,040
<Default><b>Raphy!</b></Default>

104
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,726
<Default><b>Raphtalia! Is
everything okay?</b></Default>

105
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:45,976
<Default><b>Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

106
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,379
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

107
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:50,016
<Default><b>Well, I guess that's
our cue to get going.</b></Default>

108
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,685
<Default><b>I've never been so full.</b></Default>

109
00:05:51,709 --> 00:05:54,229
<Default><b>Hey, not all of us are done
eating, you know?</b></Default>

110
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:57,170
<Default><b>[women clamoring]</b></Default>

111
00:05:57,420 --> 00:05:59,980
<Default><b>This must be what the Queen
was talking about.</b></Default>

112
00:06:00,829 --> 00:06:01,670
<Default><b><i>First off</i></b></Default>

113
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:05,709
<Default><b><i>you're going to be welcomed, and</i>
<i>then, approached by noblewomen.</i></b></Default>

114
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:09,079
<Default><b><i>After that, they'll attempt</i>
<i>to form a type of harem for you</i></b></Default>

115
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:12,290
<Default><b><i>with women from</i>
<i>any number of species.</i></b></Default>

116
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:13,830
<Default><b><i>A harem?</i></b></Default>

117
00:06:14,250 --> 00:06:15,370
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

118
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:16,660
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

119
00:06:16,829 --> 00:06:18,266
<Default><b>Great Dragon Vein</b></Default>

120
00:06:18,290 --> 00:06:20,530
<Default><b>we call upon thee
in our time of need.</b></Default>

121
00:06:20,629 --> 00:06:23,290
<Default><b>The source of thy power</b></Default>

122
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,200
<Default><b>Decipher the laws
that govern nature</b></Default>

123
00:06:26,379 --> 00:06:28,979
<Default><b>and call forth an illusion
to deceive our foes.</b></Default>

124
00:06:29,209 --> 00:06:31,000
<Default><b>Emptiness manifest form!</b></Default>

125
00:06:31,420 --> 00:06:33,170
<Default><b>[whooshing]</b></Default>

126
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:36,450
<Default><b>[squirming]</b></Default>

127
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:38,579
<Default><b>You're amazing,
Shield Hero.</b></Default>

128
00:06:38,829 --> 00:06:41,290
<Default><b>Wow! He's even stronger
than he looks.</b></Default>

129
00:06:41,709 --> 00:06:43,579
<Default><b>[women clamoring]</b></Default>

130
00:06:44,290 --> 00:06:46,890
<Default><b>What the hell kind of illusion
are they seeing?</b></Default>

131
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,646
<Default><b>Wait a second, isn't it</b></Default>

132
00:06:48,670 --> 00:06:50,670
<Default><b>"form manifest
emptiness"?</b></Default>

133
00:06:51,170 --> 00:06:53,420
<Default><b>Master Naofumi,
are you okay?</b></Default>

134
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:54,540
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

135
00:06:55,290 --> 00:06:58,129
<Default><b>Oh, why? I came when
I heard the SOS signal.</b></Default>

136
00:06:58,329 --> 00:06:59,516
<Default><b>What's going on here?</b></Default>

137
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:02,170
<Default><b>Exactly what it looks like.
An emergency.</b></Default>

138
00:07:02,379 --> 00:07:03,629
<Default><b>Oh my.</b></Default>

139
00:07:03,750 --> 00:07:05,555
<Default><b>You seem to be
enjoying yourself.</b></Default>

140
00:07:05,579 --> 00:07:07,685
<Default><b>Shoot, they got to you
ahead of me.</b></Default>

141
00:07:07,709 --> 00:07:09,629
<Default><b>They're seeing
an illusion</b></Default>

142
00:07:10,750 --> 00:07:12,550
<Default><b>Now let's get
out of here.</b></Default>

143
00:07:16,209 --> 00:07:18,249
<Default><b>You've got
some explaining to do.</b></Default>

144
00:07:18,379 --> 00:07:20,629
<Default><b>I'm truly sorry
if they troubled you.</b></Default>

145
00:07:20,709 --> 00:07:22,266
<Default><b>It's a service
we've provided</b></Default>

146
00:07:22,290 --> 00:07:24,450
<Default><b>for the Shield Hero
for generations.</b></Default>

147
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:26,580
<Default><b>I had assumed
you would enjoy it.</b></Default>

148
00:07:26,709 --> 00:07:28,709
<Default><b>Are you insulting me
right now?</b></Default>

149
00:07:28,790 --> 00:07:30,390
<Default><b>Not in the slightest.</b></Default>

150
00:07:30,459 --> 00:07:32,379
<Default><b>Please, forgive me</b></Default>

151
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:34,220
<Default><b>Enough empty apologies.</b></Default>

152
00:07:34,540 --> 00:07:36,305
<Default><b>If you want
my forgiveness</b></Default>

153
00:07:36,329 --> 00:07:38,809
<Default><b>then you'll get me
on that boat to Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

154
00:07:39,379 --> 00:07:40,476
<Default><b>Yes, of course.</b></Default>

155
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:42,605
<Default><b>We'll hold a conference
within a few days</b></Default>

156
00:07:42,629 --> 00:07:44,266
<Default><b>where we'll vote
on the matter.</b></Default>

157
00:07:44,290 --> 00:07:45,646
<Default><b>If it takes
you that long</b></Default>

158
00:07:45,670 --> 00:07:49,170
<Default><b>I suppose I'll just have to head
back home using my portal skill.</b></Default>

159
00:07:49,250 --> 00:07:50,976
<Default><b>Please, you
must be patient.</b></Default>

160
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,160
<Default><b>All I require is
a little more time.</b></Default>

161
00:07:53,209 --> 00:07:55,185
<Default><b>I promise I'll have
a ship for you.</b></Default>

162
00:07:55,209 --> 00:07:56,605
<Default><b>All right, fine.</b></Default>

163
00:07:56,629 --> 00:07:59,579
<Default><b>That said, if you keep
treating us like this</b></Default>

164
00:07:59,790 --> 00:08:02,829
<Default><b>don't be surprised if we do
something about it.</b></Default>

165
00:08:07,329 --> 00:08:09,129
<Default><b>I just don't
trust Werner.</b></Default>

166
00:08:09,629 --> 00:08:11,909
<Default><b>Who knows if he can
even get us a ship.</b></Default>

167
00:08:11,959 --> 00:08:12,959
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

168
00:08:14,209 --> 00:08:16,209
<Default><b>[suspense tones]</b></Default>

169
00:08:17,420 --> 00:08:18,579
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

170
00:08:25,709 --> 00:08:26,949
<Default><b>[chattering]</b></Default>

171
00:08:34,629 --> 00:08:36,629
<Default><b>[♪ Fun, elegant music]</b></Default>

172
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:40,039
<Default><b>Oh my!
What a magnificent outfit.</b></Default>

173
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:43,420
<Default><b>That outfit must have some
deeper meaning to it, right?</b></Default>

174
00:08:43,460 --> 00:08:45,669
<Default><b>Tell me
everything about it</b></Default>

175
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:47,419
<Default><b>[giggling]</b></Default>

176
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:51,960
<Default><b>Attention! The glorious worship
ceremony has come to an end.</b></Default>

177
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:52,879
<Default><b>However</b></Default>

178
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:56,330
<Default><b>our pleasant evening of dinner
and sweets has just begun.</b></Default>

179
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:58,159
<Default><b>[crowd gasps]</b></Default>

180
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:07,806
<Default><b>I can go and put a plate
together for you if you want.</b></Default>

181
00:09:07,830 --> 00:09:09,330
<Default><b>Sure. Sounds nice.</b></Default>

182
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:10,540
<Default><b>Thanks.</b></Default>

183
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:11,580
<Default><b>[giggling]</b></Default>

184
00:09:11,669 --> 00:09:13,389
<Default><b>Did somebody say "food"?</b></Default>

185
00:09:16,039 --> 00:09:17,789
<Default><b>[guests whispering]</b></Default>

186
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:20,960
<Default><b>Don't pay attention to them
so much, big brother.</b></Default>

187
00:09:21,210 --> 00:09:23,330
<Default><b>Atla's giving you
some good advice.</b></Default>

188
00:09:25,129 --> 00:09:26,765
<Default><b>Just try and keep
your head up.</b></Default>

189
00:09:26,789 --> 00:09:28,960
<Default><b>It's a rare opportunity</b></Default>

190
00:09:29,210 --> 00:09:30,570
<Default><b>An opportunity?</b></Default>

191
00:09:30,710 --> 00:09:33,500
<Default><b>Nothing is as it seems.
Just take a look around.</b></Default>

192
00:09:33,879 --> 00:09:34,976
<Default><b>This is supposed</b></Default>

193
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,919
<Default><b>to be an elegant banquet
to worship the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

194
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:41,330
<Default><b>But there must be some people
that are here for other reasons.</b></Default>

195
00:09:41,539 --> 00:09:43,556
<Default><b>And if you were
to find those people</b></Default>

196
00:09:43,580 --> 00:09:46,500
<Default><b>I have a feeling this party
would be over in no time.</b></Default>

197
00:09:46,580 --> 00:09:47,379
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

198
00:09:47,460 --> 00:09:49,500
<Default><b>Can I get another
drink, please?</b></Default>

199
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:53,080
<Default><b>People here for
other reasons, huh?</b></Default>

200
00:09:54,419 --> 00:09:55,539
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

201
00:09:57,710 --> 00:09:59,186
<Default><b>[JARALIS] Shield Hero.</b></Default>

202
00:09:59,210 --> 00:10:02,460
<Default><b>Are you enjoying the party
as much as it seems you are?</b></Default>

203
00:10:03,129 --> 00:10:04,329
<Default><b>I know you.</b></Default>

204
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:06,279
<Default><b>Jaralis, right?</b></Default>

205
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,476
<Default><b>Words can't describe
how pleased I am</b></Default>

206
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:10,750
<Default><b>to know you remembered
my name.</b></Default>

207
00:10:11,250 --> 00:10:13,210
<Default><b>About our discussion
yesterday…</b></Default>

208
00:10:17,460 --> 00:10:18,556
<Default><b>Fohl. Atla.</b></Default>

209
00:10:18,580 --> 00:10:19,620
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

210
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,840
<Default><b>I need to
speak with you.</b></Default>

211
00:10:26,330 --> 00:10:27,650
<Default><b>Wait a second.</b></Default>

212
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,765
<Default><b>It's been a
while, hasn't it?</b></Default>

213
00:10:40,789 --> 00:10:41,989
<Default><b>Many years.</b></Default>

214
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:44,960
<Default><b>Look at you two.
You've both grown so much.</b></Default>

215
00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:46,740
<Default><b>It is you.</b></Default>

216
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:48,879
<Default><b>You know this
man? Who is he?</b></Default>

217
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:51,400
<Default><b>But of course.
Ethan worked for our father.</b></Default>

218
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,936
<Default><b>Worked for our father?</b></Default>

219
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,960
<Default><b>Yep.</b></Default>

220
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,056
<Default><b>You may not remember
this very well</b></Default>

221
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,265
<Default><b>but Ethan used to stop</b></Default>

222
00:10:57,289 --> 00:10:59,729
<Default><b>by our house and play
with us all the time.</b></Default>

223
00:11:00,250 --> 00:11:02,710
<Default><b>Your parents died</b></Default>

224
00:11:02,789 --> 00:11:05,629
<Default><b>I've been worried sick thinking
about the two of you.</b></Default>

225
00:11:06,210 --> 00:11:08,490
<Default><b>Seeing you here now
certainly calms me.</b></Default>

226
00:11:09,210 --> 00:11:10,476
<Default><b>As you've witnessed</b></Default>

227
00:11:10,500 --> 00:11:12,379
<Default><b>us white tiger
Demi-humans</b></Default>

228
00:11:12,460 --> 00:11:15,186
<Default><b>are often looked down upon
by others in this country.</b></Default>

229
00:11:15,210 --> 00:11:16,650
<Default><b>It's humiliating.</b></Default>

230
00:11:16,789 --> 00:11:19,750
<Default><b>However, there is something
urgent I had to tell you.</b></Default>

231
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,240
<Default><b>[swallowing]</b></Default>

232
00:11:23,039 --> 00:11:25,710
<Default><b>The two of you should avoid
Jaralis, the lion.</b></Default>

233
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,120
<Default><b>You see</b></Default>

234
00:11:27,460 --> 00:11:30,460
<Default><b>it's suspected that he had
a hand in your father's death.</b></Default>

235
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:32,910
<Default><b>Seriously?</b></Default>

236
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:34,515
<Default><b>Rumor has it</b></Default>

237
00:11:34,539 --> 00:11:37,289
<Default><b>he was present during
your father's last moments.</b></Default>

238
00:11:37,379 --> 00:11:38,726
<Default><b>That being said</b></Default>

239
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:41,605
<Default><b>people in the military that
claim this rumor to be false.</b></Default>

240
00:11:41,629 --> 00:11:42,895
<Default><b>Well, was it?</b></Default>

241
00:11:42,919 --> 00:11:43,669
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

242
00:11:43,830 --> 00:11:46,895
<Default><b>His report of Master Turen's
last moments didn't make sense.</b></Default>

243
00:11:46,919 --> 00:11:49,039
<Default><b>I told the military
to investigate.</b></Default>

244
00:11:49,419 --> 00:11:50,806
<Default><b>But they refused</b></Default>

245
00:11:50,830 --> 00:11:53,210
<Default><b>claiming they already
looked into things.</b></Default>

246
00:11:54,289 --> 00:11:55,419
<Default><b>Even now</b></Default>

247
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:58,879
<Default><b>I regret not fighting with
Master Turen until the end.</b></Default>

248
00:11:59,289 --> 00:12:01,609
<Default><b>I should have been there
to protect him.</b></Default>

249
00:12:03,539 --> 00:12:06,500
<Default><b>But now, I have a chance
to atone for my sins</b></Default>

250
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:09,539
<Default><b>by doing whatever I can
to help his children.</b></Default>

251
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:13,129
<Default><b>Know that I'm here
to serve you however I can.</b></Default>

252
00:12:14,289 --> 00:12:16,015
<Default><b>So, are things
proceeding well</b></Default>

253
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:18,419
<Default><b>with Lord Werner
concerning your ship?</b></Default>

254
00:12:19,919 --> 00:12:20,976
<Default><b>As I thought.</b></Default>

255
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,556
<Default><b>Werner has little to no desire
to do something</b></Default>

256
00:12:23,580 --> 00:12:26,500
<Default><b>like summon you a ship
if it would mean you're leaving.</b></Default>

257
00:12:26,710 --> 00:12:29,379
<Default><b>After all, the longer
he keeps you here</b></Default>

258
00:12:29,460 --> 00:12:31,860
<Default><b>the more favor he garners
from the masses.</b></Default>

259
00:12:32,210 --> 00:12:35,090
<Default><b>Public opinion is very important
for someone like him.</b></Default>

260
00:12:35,169 --> 00:12:36,895
<Default><b>Why does it
even matter at all?</b></Default>

261
00:12:36,919 --> 00:12:39,355
<Default><b>Because the people's faith
in the Shield Hero is</b></Default>

262
00:12:39,379 --> 00:12:41,179
<Default><b>so strong in
this country.</b></Default>

263
00:12:41,379 --> 00:12:43,056
<Default><b>People began
asking themselves</b></Default>

264
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,210
<Default><b>why you protect
other nations</b></Default>

265
00:12:45,289 --> 00:12:48,329
<Default><b>as opposed to protecting the
place where you're worshipped</b></Default>

266
00:12:48,379 --> 00:12:49,080
<Default><b>Siltvelt.</b></Default>

267
00:12:49,169 --> 00:12:50,186
<Default><b>You see</b></Default>

268
00:12:50,210 --> 00:12:53,410
<Default><b>more and more people here are
beginning to share that thought.</b></Default>

269
00:12:54,129 --> 00:12:55,186
<Default><b>Werner's concern</b></Default>

270
00:12:55,210 --> 00:12:57,395
<Default><b>is that the people who
share this sentiment</b></Default>

271
00:12:57,419 --> 00:13:00,539
<Default><b>might do something rash if the
opportunity presented itself.</b></Default>

272
00:13:01,629 --> 00:13:02,419
<Default><b>Which means</b></Default>

273
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:05,539
<Default><b>no matter what
you say to him</b></Default>

274
00:13:05,669 --> 00:13:06,989
<Default><b>[disagreement]</b></Default>

275
00:13:07,169 --> 00:13:10,379
<Default><b>However, I'm offering you myself
as an alternative.</b></Default>

276
00:13:10,710 --> 00:13:13,879
<Default><b>Say the word and I'll arrange
a ship to Q'ten Lo for you.</b></Default>

277
00:13:15,250 --> 00:13:17,850
<Default><b>Unfortunately, I'm not able
to do so officially</b></Default>

278
00:13:17,919 --> 00:13:20,159
<Default><b>due to the limits
of my position here.</b></Default>

279
00:13:20,289 --> 00:13:21,556
<Default><b>That being said</b></Default>

280
00:13:21,580 --> 00:13:23,476
<Default><b>I'm willing to do
whatever it takes</b></Default>

281
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:26,039
<Default><b>if it means me helping out
the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

282
00:13:26,419 --> 00:13:29,019
<Default><b>You are our people's god
and this is your wish.</b></Default>

283
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:32,600
<Default><b>Believe me when I tell you
it saddens me to say</b></Default>

284
00:13:32,830 --> 00:13:35,630
<Default><b>but letting me help you is
the only way to Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

285
00:13:39,039 --> 00:13:40,439
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

286
00:13:42,919 --> 00:13:43,960
<Default><b>Wow!</b></Default>

287
00:13:44,629 --> 00:13:45,936
<Default><b>[FILO] Looks yummy.</b></Default>

288
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,145
<Default><b>It certainly does.</b></Default>

289
00:13:47,169 --> 00:13:49,855
<Default><b>[WERNER] Oh, there you are.
Good morning, Shield Hero.</b></Default>

290
00:13:49,879 --> 00:13:52,645
<Default><b>If you don't mind, I'd like you
to attend a conference</b></Default>

291
00:13:52,669 --> 00:13:54,306
<Default><b>after you've
finished eating.</b></Default>

292
00:13:54,330 --> 00:13:56,539
<Default><b>Followed by a lunch</b></Default>

293
00:13:56,629 --> 00:13:58,919
<Default><b>All right, all right.
I'll be there.</b></Default>

294
00:13:59,250 --> 00:13:59,919
<Default><b>Great.</b></Default>

295
00:14:00,169 --> 00:14:03,089
<Default><b>I will come and get you early
to show you the location.</b></Default>

296
00:14:06,789 --> 00:14:08,029
<Default><b>As expected.</b></Default>

297
00:14:08,330 --> 00:14:10,806
<Default><b>Werner keeps throwing
meaningless ceremonies</b></Default>

298
00:14:10,830 --> 00:14:13,550
<Default><b>and useless meetings my way
to keep us stuck here.</b></Default>

299
00:14:14,129 --> 00:14:16,710
<Default><b>Jaralis is
right about that</b></Default>

300
00:14:17,669 --> 00:14:20,186
<Default><b>But the way he's been sucking up
to me doesn't sit</b></Default>

301
00:14:20,210 --> 00:14:21,810
<Default><b>right with me either.</b></Default>

302
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:25,129
<Default><b>From what Fohl
and Atla told me</b></Default>

303
00:14:25,210 --> 00:14:27,650
<Default><b>it sounds like this guy
could be dangerous.</b></Default>

304
00:14:28,669 --> 00:14:29,709
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

305
00:14:30,379 --> 00:14:32,579
<Default><b>Seems neither of them
can be trusted.</b></Default>

306
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,240
<Default><b>Which means…</b></Default>

307
00:14:34,830 --> 00:14:37,210
<Default><b>Offer up your prayers
to the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

308
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:40,539
<Default><b>It is the will of the Shield God
that determines all.</b></Default>

309
00:14:40,629 --> 00:14:42,686
<Default><b>It is thanks to him
that we have food.</b></Default>

310
00:14:42,710 --> 00:14:45,039
<Default><b>It is thanks to him
that we are here.</b></Default>

311
00:14:45,210 --> 00:14:47,306
<Default><b>Let this food before us
and our lives</b></Default>

312
00:14:47,330 --> 00:14:49,450
<Default><b>become the power
to enact His will.</b></Default>

313
00:14:50,789 --> 00:14:52,349
<Default><b>Let it become power!</b></Default>

314
00:14:53,039 --> 00:14:55,559
<Default><b>Even the prayers they say
here are wonderful.</b></Default>

315
00:14:55,629 --> 00:14:57,556
<Default><b>Now then, it would be
our pleasure</b></Default>

316
00:14:57,580 --> 00:14:59,710
<Default><b>if you were to eat first</b></Default>

317
00:15:05,129 --> 00:15:08,419
<Default><b>Either way, this country
is starting to creep me out.</b></Default>

318
00:15:09,210 --> 00:15:11,330
<Default><b>I've got to find
a way out of here.</b></Default>

319
00:15:16,580 --> 00:15:19,420
<Default><b>All right. Let's bring this
special meeting to order.</b></Default>

320
00:15:20,789 --> 00:15:23,186
<Default><b>To begin, as we work
to strengthen our military</b></Default>

321
00:15:23,210 --> 00:15:25,056
<Default><b>in preparation
for the next wave</b></Default>

322
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,806
<Default><b>we need to reorganize
our forces</b></Default>

323
00:15:26,830 --> 00:15:29,806
<Default><b>with the Shield Hero at the
center in order to bring out…</b></Default>

324
00:15:29,830 --> 00:15:31,015
<Default><b>Let me stop you there.</b></Default>

325
00:15:31,039 --> 00:15:33,289
<Default><b>You talk like
I'm staying</b></Default>

326
00:15:33,379 --> 00:15:36,056
<Default><b>abundantly clear that
I'm only passing through here.</b></Default>

327
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:37,476
<Default><b>And we acknowledge that.</b></Default>

328
00:15:37,500 --> 00:15:40,220
<Default><b>Which brings me to our next
point to address here…</b></Default>

329
00:15:40,250 --> 00:15:42,855
<Default><b>The budget needed to have
our finest shipyard build</b></Default>

330
00:15:42,879 --> 00:15:44,686
<Default><b>a vessel worthy
of the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

331
00:15:44,710 --> 00:15:46,710
<Default><b>You know that's not
what I want.</b></Default>

332
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:47,790
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

333
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,226
<Default><b>Listen, I'm not stupid.</b></Default>

334
00:15:49,250 --> 00:15:52,500
<Default><b>I understand you need me to stay
right here so you can use me</b></Default>

335
00:15:52,580 --> 00:15:55,879
<Default><b>to expand your military and
unite the people of your nation.</b></Default>

336
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,040
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

337
00:15:57,460 --> 00:16:00,105
<Default><b>However, just like you want
to protect your country</b></Default>

338
00:16:00,129 --> 00:16:02,329
<Default><b>I want to protect
the lands I govern.</b></Default>

339
00:16:02,379 --> 00:16:05,419
<Default><b>The people of my village
are waiting for me to return</b></Default>

340
00:16:05,500 --> 00:16:06,605
<Default><b>as we speak.</b></Default>

341
00:16:06,629 --> 00:16:07,749
<Default><b>Yes, but…</b></Default>

342
00:16:08,330 --> 00:16:12,379
<Default><b>Look, once the Phoenix and
Q'ten Lo are dealt with, I don't</b></Default>

343
00:16:12,460 --> 00:16:15,420
<Default><b>mind acting more like the Shield
Hero you want me to be.</b></Default>

344
00:16:15,460 --> 00:16:16,879
<Default><b>[clapping]</b></Default>

345
00:16:19,039 --> 00:16:20,789
<Default><b>Spoken like a true hero.</b></Default>

346
00:16:20,879 --> 00:16:23,226
<Default><b>A ruler should
always prioritize his lands and</b></Default>

347
00:16:23,250 --> 00:16:26,210
<Default><b>people above everything else.
And in that sense</b></Default>

348
00:16:26,289 --> 00:16:29,049
<Default><b>I could learn a thing or two
from you, Shield Hero.</b></Default>

349
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,210
<Default><b>Though I'm sad you
want to leave.</b></Default>

350
00:16:31,379 --> 00:16:33,750
<Default><b>After all, I want
the same thing</b></Default>

351
00:16:33,830 --> 00:16:36,169
<Default><b>for the Shield Hero
to unite our country</b></Default>

352
00:16:36,250 --> 00:16:38,210
<Default><b>and quell
the people's worries.</b></Default>

353
00:16:38,419 --> 00:16:40,500
<Default><b>But look what
we're doing here.</b></Default>

354
00:16:40,669 --> 00:16:43,226
<Default><b>Can you not see we're ignoring
the wishes of our god</b></Default>

355
00:16:43,250 --> 00:16:45,750
<Default><b>for our own country's
self-interest?</b></Default>

356
00:16:45,919 --> 00:16:49,000
<Default><b>Shouldn't we honor his wish and
prepare a ship immediately?</b></Default>

357
00:16:49,289 --> 00:16:51,919
<Default><b>As I'm sure you're
well aware of by now</b></Default>

358
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:54,726
<Default><b>only spokesmen of the four
great races can speak here.</b></Default>

359
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:56,790
<Default><b>Please know
your place, Jaralis.</b></Default>

360
00:16:56,919 --> 00:16:57,999
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

361
00:16:58,750 --> 00:17:01,000
<Default><b>I apologize
for the inconvenience.</b></Default>

362
00:17:01,379 --> 00:17:04,829
<Default><b>Your input on this matter is
very valuable to all of us here.</b></Default>

363
00:17:05,130 --> 00:17:07,186
<Default><b>Please give us some
more time, so that</b></Default>

364
00:17:07,210 --> 00:17:10,146
<Default><b>we may put together our thoughts
in light of your opinion.</b></Default>

365
00:17:10,170 --> 00:17:11,650
<Default><b><i>Yet another delay.</i></b></Default>

366
00:17:12,079 --> 00:17:14,119
<Default><b><i>Just how hard-headed</i>
<i>is this guy?</i></b></Default>

367
00:17:19,329 --> 00:17:21,289
<Default><b>[hammer strikes]</b></Default>

368
00:17:22,380 --> 00:17:23,039
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

369
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:24,490
<Default><b>Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

370
00:17:25,039 --> 00:17:27,519
<Default><b>Let's do this quickly
while nobody's around.</b></Default>

371
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:28,960
<Default><b>Mmhm.</b></Default>

372
00:17:29,460 --> 00:17:32,380
<Default><b>This is Ethan, the person
that I was telling you about.</b></Default>

373
00:17:32,829 --> 00:17:34,726
<Default><b>It's such an
honor to meet you.</b></Default>

374
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:37,070
<Default><b>You have my thanks
for saving these two.</b></Default>

375
00:17:37,420 --> 00:17:40,579
<Default><b>Please know you've done
more than I can ever repay</b></Default>

376
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:43,210
<Default><b>and so I'll be forever
in your debt.</b></Default>

377
00:17:43,539 --> 00:17:46,539
<Default><b>I'll do anything. Anything
if it means helping you two.</b></Default>

378
00:17:46,630 --> 00:17:47,950
<Default><b>That's enough.</b></Default>

379
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,960
<Default><b>I did it because
I wanted to.</b></Default>

380
00:17:50,670 --> 00:17:53,789
<Default><b>In any case, Fohl told you
what I needed, right?</b></Default>

381
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,600
<Default><b>Yes, to keep a watchful eye
on the two of them.</b></Default>

382
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:57,500
<Default><b>Correct.</b></Default>

383
00:17:57,710 --> 00:17:59,726
<Default><b>Werner and Jaralis
are a problem.</b></Default>

384
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:02,790
<Default><b>They'll both try to break out
of the stalemate they're in…</b></Default>

385
00:18:02,829 --> 00:18:05,146
<Default><b>Which means they might
do something rash.</b></Default>

386
00:18:05,170 --> 00:18:07,555
<Default><b>Share any information you get
with these guys.</b></Default>

387
00:18:07,579 --> 00:18:08,579
<Default><b>Hello!</b></Default>

388
00:18:08,750 --> 00:18:10,190
<Default><b>Nice to meet you.</b></Default>

389
00:18:10,289 --> 00:18:13,670
<Default><b>And in just a few days</b></Default>

390
00:18:15,710 --> 00:18:16,710
<Default><b>Wow.</b></Default>

391
00:18:17,170 --> 00:18:21,000
<Default><b>On the surface, I played along
with their stalling tactics</b></Default>

392
00:18:21,079 --> 00:18:23,079
<Default><b>while I prepared
in secret.</b></Default>

393
00:18:24,329 --> 00:18:26,750
<Default><b>So that I'd be ready
when the time came.</b></Default>

394
00:18:29,289 --> 00:18:32,920
<Default><b>And thus, my days
in Siltvelt passed by.</b></Default>

395
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:44,170
<Default><b>POISON DETECTED</b></Default>

396
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,630
<Default><b>It's not yummy anymore.</b></Default>

397
00:18:47,750 --> 00:18:48,579
<Default><b>Really?</b></Default>

398
00:18:48,670 --> 00:18:49,765
<Default><b>I, on the other hand</b></Default>

399
00:18:49,789 --> 00:18:52,356
<Default><b>will eat anything as long
as there's beer with it.</b></Default>

400
00:18:52,380 --> 00:18:53,039
<Default><b>That's gross.</b></Default>

401
00:18:53,130 --> 00:18:55,805
<Default><b>The will of the Shield God
determines everything.</b></Default>

402
00:18:55,829 --> 00:18:57,805
<Default><b>It is thanks to him
that we have food.</b></Default>

403
00:18:57,829 --> 00:18:59,805
<Default><b>It is thanks to him
that we're here.</b></Default>

404
00:18:59,829 --> 00:19:02,106
<Default><b>Let this food before us and
our lives become</b></Default>

405
00:19:02,130 --> 00:19:04,250
<Default><b>the power to
enact His will.</b></Default>

406
00:19:04,329 --> 00:19:05,889
<Default><b>Let it become power!</b></Default>

407
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:08,960
<Default><b>Shield Hero, please eat
before the rest of us.</b></Default>

408
00:19:13,579 --> 00:19:14,659
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

409
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:28,400
<Default><b>[crowd coughing]</b></Default>

410
00:19:30,289 --> 00:19:32,649
<Default><b>Shield Hero, what is
the meaning of this?</b></Default>

411
00:19:32,920 --> 00:19:34,476
<Default><b>Just shut up
and drink it.</b></Default>

412
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:37,540
<Default><b>It tastes like shit, but it's
better than dying of poison.</b></Default>

413
00:19:38,130 --> 00:19:39,170
<Default><b>Poison?</b></Default>

414
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:42,686
<Default><b>So he's playing
dumb, huh?</b></Default>

415
00:19:42,710 --> 00:19:45,710
<Default><b>To poison a god is a crime
worthy of death.</b></Default>

416
00:19:45,789 --> 00:19:47,269
<Default><b>It is blasphemous.</b></Default>

417
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:50,186
<Default><b>What's with the look?</b></Default>

418
00:19:50,210 --> 00:19:52,010
<Default><b>Have something
to tell me?</b></Default>

419
00:19:52,710 --> 00:19:54,015
<Default><b>All right, relax.</b></Default>

420
00:19:54,039 --> 00:19:55,856
<Default><b>Seeing as you all
love to chitchat</b></Default>

421
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:58,539
<Default><b>what do you say we sit down
and talk about this?</b></Default>

422
00:19:58,630 --> 00:19:59,790
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

423
00:20:03,329 --> 00:20:05,849
<Default><b>To think that someone would
try poisoning me.</b></Default>

424
00:20:06,289 --> 00:20:09,329
<Default><b>I thought this country of yours
was supposed to be safe.</b></Default>

425
00:20:09,420 --> 00:20:12,210
<Default><b>There's no doubt in my mind
that Jaralis did this.</b></Default>

426
00:20:12,380 --> 00:20:15,880
<Default><b>Only he would do something as
shallow as betraying our own God</b></Default>

427
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:19,329
<Default><b>Without proof, I'm afraid your
words are as empty as your head.</b></Default>

428
00:20:19,420 --> 00:20:21,856
<Default><b>For all we know, you could
have done it because</b></Default>

429
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:24,226
<Default><b>you knew the Shield Hero
was leaving our lands.</b></Default>

430
00:20:24,250 --> 00:20:26,250
<Default><b>It makes sense
now, doesn't it?</b></Default>

431
00:20:26,460 --> 00:20:27,460
<Default><b>Liar.</b></Default>

432
00:20:28,210 --> 00:20:31,170
<Default><b>Well, I don't
care who did it</b></Default>

433
00:20:31,329 --> 00:20:34,210
<Default><b>All that matters is someone
tried poisoning us.</b></Default>

434
00:20:34,710 --> 00:20:36,356
<Default><b>To me, it's
unforgivable.</b></Default>

435
00:20:36,380 --> 00:20:39,500
<Default><b>I can't cooperate with a country
that tries poisoning me.</b></Default>

436
00:20:40,210 --> 00:20:42,380
<Default><b>Plus, I've got a
lead on a boat.</b></Default>

437
00:20:42,789 --> 00:20:45,646
<Default><b>I'm not going to entertain your
shenanigans any longer.</b></Default>

438
00:20:45,670 --> 00:20:47,555
<Default><b>You can't, Shield Hero.
Please.</b></Default>

439
00:20:47,579 --> 00:20:50,106
<Default><b>You've only yourself to blame
for this, Werner.</b></Default>

440
00:20:50,130 --> 00:20:53,250
<Default><b>You've upset our God and lost a
chance to help him out.</b></Default>

441
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:56,210
<Default><b>I would go so far as
to call this blasphemous.</b></Default>

442
00:20:56,539 --> 00:20:59,670
<Default><b>That's quite the failure you
have on your name, Werner.</b></Default>

443
00:20:59,750 --> 00:21:01,476
<Default><b>Know your
place, Jaralis.</b></Default>

444
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:04,106
<Default><b>I knew that you were up to
something underhanded.</b></Default>

445
00:21:04,130 --> 00:21:05,000
<Default><b>If you say</b></Default>

446
00:21:05,079 --> 00:21:07,750
<Default><b>I'm responsible for this</b></Default>

447
00:21:07,829 --> 00:21:10,289
<Default><b>To make such an accusation
is unforgivable.</b></Default>

448
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:14,039
<Default><b>Everything you've done up until
now is all the proof that I need</b></Default>

449
00:21:14,130 --> 00:21:17,010
<Default><b>I know you'd do anything
if it meant you'd gain power.</b></Default>

450
00:21:17,079 --> 00:21:19,436
<Default><b>I'm not the only one
who's able to see that.</b></Default>

451
00:21:19,460 --> 00:21:20,170
<Default><b>I knew it.</b></Default>

452
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:21,000
<Default><b>He's right.</b></Default>

453
00:21:21,079 --> 00:21:21,630
<Default><b>Coward.</b></Default>

454
00:21:21,710 --> 00:21:22,289
<Default><b>Shameful.</b></Default>

455
00:21:22,380 --> 00:21:24,976
<Default><b>You're only doing this because
you're in danger.</b></Default>

456
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:27,460
<Default><b>Or should I say
your position's in danger?</b></Default>

457
00:21:27,539 --> 00:21:31,079
<Default><b>Is this any way for a ruler
to be acting amidst a crisis?</b></Default>

458
00:21:31,250 --> 00:21:32,305
<Default><b>This is what happens</b></Default>

459
00:21:32,329 --> 00:21:35,289
<Default><b>when you let bloodlines decide
who gets to be in charge.</b></Default>

460
00:21:35,630 --> 00:21:37,476
<Default><b>There are many
talented people</b></Default>

461
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:40,380
<Default><b>outside of the four great races
who are fit to lead.</b></Default>

462
00:21:40,460 --> 00:21:41,606
<Default><b>[laughter]</b></Default>

463
00:21:41,630 --> 00:21:44,310
<Default><b>How embarrassing
if you're referring to yourself.</b></Default>

464
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:45,686
<Default><b>What was that?</b></Default>

465
00:21:45,710 --> 00:21:47,030
<Default><b>Shut up, Laio.</b></Default>

466
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:50,880
<Default><b>[fighting]</b></Default>

467
00:21:53,250 --> 00:21:54,829
<Default><b>All of you, shut up.</b></Default>

468
00:22:01,710 --> 00:22:04,190
<Default><b>I'm not listening
to another second of this.</b></Default>

469
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:06,750
<Default><b>[♪ Closing music begins]</b></Default>

470
00:23:32,630 --> 00:23:34,329
<Default><b>[♪ Closing music ends]</b></Default>

471
00:23:36,539 --> 00:23:40,039
<Default><b>A TRUE PEOPLE</b></Default>

